name: HipFracture
title: Hip Fracture
description:
Used to identify patients with fracture of hip or in the region of the hip.
NOTE:  VALUE SET UNDER DEVELOPMENT AS MEASURE TESTING IS ONGOING.
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains codes that identify patients with fracture of hip or in the region of the hip.),(Data Element Scope: Using the Quality Data Model, this particular element would map to the Diagnosis category or the Diagnosis attribute for the Encounter category),(Inclusion Criteria: Include all diagnosis codes associated with  pelvis, femur, hip fracture regardless of type of fracture (i.e., stress, pathological, avulsion, etc.)),(Exclusion Criteria: None)
